data.description: SHOWS LIKE A MODEL HOME! This home is spectacular w/ custom features that are breathtaking!  Additional square footage was added in the living areas w/ an open sunroom looking out to the covered patio. The breakfast area was also extended to accommodate a large seating area. The details in the home are evident in the kitchen w/ 12’x4’ Carrara marble island including 2 sinks, 2 dishwashers, 2 dual trash pull outs & seating for four. The chef-selected GE Monogram Appliances include a 48-inch built in refrigerator, double convection ovens, 6 burner gas range w/ griddle plus lighted gas knobs & pot filler! Pull out drawers in cabinets, sectioned drawers plus huge walk-in pantry are show stoppers! Primary suite has gorgeous crystal lighting, door to the patio & primary bath w/ amazing shower. All bedrooms have ensuite bathrooms. Second floor media room is fully equipped! Enjoy additional living space outdoors w/ gas fireplace, gas grill, 2 burners, pizza oven, speakers, plus a pool bath!
